# Marlin Doc
##### EZ3-India

# cardreader

 **CardReader::CardReader() **
  + Defines public CardReader method
  + Initialisaiton of printer status flags
  + Which are further used in other CardReader methods
___
 **char \*createFilename(char *buffer,const dir_t &p)**
  + Limit the file name to 12 characters
___
**void CardReader::lsDive(const char *prepend, SdFile parent, const char * const match/*=NULL*/)**
  + Dive into a folder and recurse depth-first to perform a pre-set operation lsAction:
 *   LS_Count       - Add +1 to nrFiles for every file within the parent
 *   LS_GetFilename - Get the filename of the file indexed by nrFiles
 *   LS_SerialPrint - Print the full path of each file to serial output
___
**void CardReader::ls()**
  + lists all files to Serial Out
___
**void CardReader::initsd()**
  + Initializes SDcard and sets the ROOT dir
___
**void CardReader::setroot()**
  + Sets Current Dir to ROOT
___
**void CardReader::release()**
  + Set flags before SD/Print release
___
**void CardReader::startFileprint()**
  + Set Printing Flag to true
___
**void CardReader::pauseSDPrint()**
  + Set Printing Flag to false
___
**void CardReader::openLogFile(char* name)**
  + 
